high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the grey bin in between the sink and fridge.
Pick up the bread from inside the bin.
Take a step to the right to face the fridge.
Place the bread inside the fridge for it to cool and then take it back out.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave above the stove.
Place the bread inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the cool bread inside the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk straight toward the trash bin
Pick up the loaf of bread out of the trash bin
Turn to the right and face the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and put the bread inside, chill then remove the bread
Turn to the left and walk to the stove
Open the microwave above the stove  and place the bread inside
Turn around and go to the trash can.
Take the bread from the trash can.
Turn around, then go left, and then turn left again to go to the fridge.
Chill the bread in the fridge.
Turn around, go straight, then turn right to go to the stove.
Put the bread in the microwave above the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put cold bread in the microwave.
